    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
      <head>Scope and Content
</head>
      <p>Halifax County (Va.) Various Court Records, ca. 1764-ca. 1800. Consists of petitions from the debt cases Matthew Marable vs. Patrick Bradie, n.d., William Astin vs. Abraham  Ardin, n.d., and Thomas Billings vs. Elizabeth Billings, 1764; a bill from the chancery case, Obadiah Smith vs. Solomon Sizemore, etc., 1800; and a land partition suit, John Roberts and Mary Roberts vs. Orphans of Matthew Sims, 1791.
</p>
    </scopecontent>
